snippet.title: Overwatch 2 x My Hero Academia | Collaboration Trailer
snippet.description:
Unleash your inner hero or villain in Overwatch 2 x My Hero Academia!

The legendary characters from U.A. High School are making their way to Future Earth. Will you stand with the heroes and battle injustice or side with the villains and create endless chaos?

Show the world your bravery and skill when Overwatch 2 x My Hero Academia arrives Oct 17.

Overwatch 2 is free to play for everyone on console & PC!

© K. Horikoshi / Shueisha, My Hero Academia Project
